{"tid":1938544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真心，不如放棄抗疫算","createTime":"2020-03-22T15:17:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T05:46:05.000Z","uid":120847,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3f7b87e086c836ded5efe99215053b49e02f40ed","tid":1938544,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"呢個病毒唔係咁簡單，傳染力極強<br />\n根本㩒都㩒唔住<br />\n依加好多國家都停工停市停學<br />\n咁搞落去個病未殺死大家 大家都已經餓死<br />\n<br />\n其實遲早都有疫苗同藥 可能呢段過渡期會死人<br />\n但遲早都會過<br />\n不如復工復市，叫政府咪撚派錢，轉派消費券鼓勵消費<br />\n到時全世界都百廢待興時 我地香港就no.1<br />\n<br />\n利申唔係講笑唔係曲 真心"},{"pid":"12bcf8a67e0c0e004f812fd6c4c7cff5e577c350","tid":1938544,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:18:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9773b7a5b310bf13aec0e70b1347cce4baa45cb2","tid":1938544,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3168488d090a343b2a513c0ca57afb8eb3853989","tid":1938544,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:22:47.000Z","msg":"說好的攬炒呢?"},{"pid":"b0cd25d26eb30cdd06aa22c95d37baaa20c61f2e","tid":1938544,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T05:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}